<body>

<% include ../templates/navigation.ejs %>
<main>
    <div class="section no-pad-bot" id="index-banner">
        <div class="container">
            <br><br>
            <h1 class="header center <%= customColor1 %>-text">pStats</h1>
            <div class="row center">
                <h5 class="header col s12 light">Plugin Metrics Stats</h5>
            </div>
            <br><br>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="container">
        <!--   Icon Section   -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
                <div class="icon-block">
                    <h2 class="center red-text"><i class="material-icons">assessment</i></h2>
                    <h5 class="center">Plugin Metrics</h5>

                    <p class="center light">pStats allows you to collect usage data for your Bukkit, Spigot, Bungeecord or Sponge plugin.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
                <div class="icon-block">
                    <h2 class="center red-text"><i class="material-icons">storage</i></h2>
                    <h5 class="center">Hosted by HumbleServers</h5>

                    <p class="center light">We are happy to be sponsored by <a href="https://a.devs.beer/humble">HumbleServers</a>!<br>
                        You should definitely check out their website!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
                <div class="icon-block">
                    <h2 class="center red-text"><i class="material-icons">schedule</i></h2>
                    <h5 class="center">Integrated within seconds</h5>

                    <p class="center light">pStats is extremely easy to integrate into your plugin.<br>
                        Just add one class to your plugin and you are done!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
                <div class="icon-block">
                    <h2 class="center red-text"><i class="material-icons">trending_up</i></h2>
                    <h5 class="center">Lightning fast</h5>

                    <p class="center light">pStats is optimized for performance and stability.<br>It's extremely reliable, scalable and still super fast. Say goodbye to slow response times!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
                <div class="icon-block">
                    <h2 class="center red-text"><i class="material-icons">code</i></h2>
                    <h5 class="center">Open source</h5>

                    <p class="center light">pStats is completely open source! Feel free to check out our <a href="https://github.com/Bastian/pStats">GitHub page</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
                <div class="icon-block">
                    <h2 class="center"><img alt="Discord" src="/images/discord.svg"></h2>
                    <h5 class="center">Join our Discord</h5>

                    <p class="center light">
                        Keep up to date with the development of my software
                        or just chat with other community users on <a href="https://a.devs.beer/pstats-discord">Discord</a>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br><br>
</main>
